\c 22
\s Imilayo ngezinye izinto
\p
\v 1 Awuyikubona inkabi yomfowenu\x + Eks. 23.4.\x* loba imvu yakhe iduha, uzicatshele. Uzazibuyisela lokuzibuyisela kumfowenu\x + Eks. 12.3.\x*.
\v 2 Njalo uba umfowenu engekho eduze lawe, loba ungamazi, uzayiletha-ke phakathi komuzi wakho; njalo izakuba kuwe, umfowenu aze ayidinge, ubusuyibuyisela kuye.
\v 3 Wenze njalo langobabhemi wakhe, wenze njalo langesembatho sakhe, wenze njalo langayo yonke into elahlekileyo yomfowenu, ayilahlileyo, oyitholileyo; awulakuyicatshela.
\p
\v 4 Awuyikubona ubabhemi womfowenu loba inkabi yakhe kusiwa endleleni, ukucatshele; uzakuphakamisa lokukuphakamisa kanye laye\x + Eks. 23.5.\x*.
\p
\v 5 Owesifazana angagqoki okwendoda, lendoda ingagqoki isigqoko sowesifazana; ngoba wonke owenza lezizinto uyisinengiso eN\nd kosi\nd*ni uNkulunkulu wakho.
\p
\v 6 Uba kungaba lesidleke senyoni phambi kwakho endleleni loba kusiphi isihlahla loba phansi, amaphuphu kumbe amaqanda, unina efukamele amaphuphu loba amaqanda, ungathathi unina lamaphuphu\x + Levi 22.28.\x*;
\v 7 uzayekela lokuyekela unina ukuze ahambe, uzithathele amaphuphu, ukuze kukulungele, njalo welule insuku\x + 4.40.\x*.
\p
\v 8 Nxa usakha indlu entsha, uzakwenzela uphahla lwakho uthango, ukuze ungayehliseli indlu yakho icala legazi, uba umuntu esiwa awe kulo.
\p
\v 9 Ungahlanyeli inhlobo ezimbili esivinini sakho, hlezi isivuno esigcweleyo senhlanyelo yakho oyihlanyeleyo lesithelo sesivini singcoliswe\x + Levi 19.19.\x*.
\p
\v 10 Ungalimi ngenkabi lobabhemi ndawonye.
\p
\v 11 Ungagqoki isigqoko esixubene\x + Levi 19.19.\x*, uboya bezimvu lelembu elicolekileyo ndawonye\x + Levi 13.47,48.\x*.
\p
\v 12 Uzazenzela\x + Nani 15.38.\x* intshaka emiphethweni yomine yesembatho sakho ozembesa ngaso\x + 1 Kho. 7.17.\x*.
\s Imilayo emayelana lokuthatha umfazi
\p
\v 13 Uba indoda ithatha umfazi, ingene kuye, ibisimzonda,
\v 14 imbeke icala elilehlazo, imgcone ngebizo elibi, ithi: Ngathatha lowesifazana; lapho ngisondela kuye kangitholanga ubuntombi kuye.
\v 15 Uyise wentombi lonina bazathatha baveze ubufakazi bobuntombi bentombi ebadaleni bomuzi esangweni.
\v 16 Loyise wentombi uzakuthi ebadaleni: Ngendisela indodakazi yami kulindoda; yasiyizonda;
\v 17 khangelani-ke, ibeke icala elilehlazo, isithi: Kangitholanga ubuntombi endodakazini yakho. Kanti lobu yibufakazi bobuntombi bendodakazi yami. Besebesendlala ilembu phambi kwabadala bomuzi.
\v 18 Abadala balowomuzi babesebethatha leyondoda bayijezise;
\v 19 bamhlawulise inhlamvu zesiliva ezilikhulu, bazinike uyise wentombi, ngoba iveze ibizo elibi phezu kwentombi emsulwa yakoIsrayeli. Njalo izakuba ngumkayo; kayilakuyilahla zonke izinsuku zayo.
\v 20 Kodwa uba linto iliqiniso; ubufakazi bobuntombi kabutholakalanga entombini,
\v 21 intombi bazayikhuphela emnyango wendlu kayise\x + Gen. 34.7.\x*, lamadoda omuzi wayo ayikhande ngamatshe ize ife; ngoba yenzile ubuphukuphuku koIsrayeli ngokwenza ubuwule endlini kayise. Ngalokhu uzakhupha ububi phakathi kwakho\x + 13.5.\x*.
\p
\v 22 Uba indoda ificwa ilele lomfazi owendele endodeni, labo bobabili bazakufa-ke, indoda ebilele lomfazi, lalowomfazi\x + Levi 20.10. Joha. 8.5.\x*. Ngalokhu uzakhupha ububi koIsrayeli\x + 13.5.\x*.
\p
\v 23 Uba kulentombazana eyintombi emsulwa egane indoda, njalo indoda iyithole phakathi komuzi, ilale layo\x + Mat. 1.18,19.\x*,
\v 24 lizabakhuphela esangweni lalowomuzi bobabili, libakhande ngamatshe baze bafe; intombi ngoba ingahlabanga umkhosi phakathi komuzi, lendoda ngoba ithobise umkamakhelwane wakhe\x + 21.14.\x*. Ngalokhu uzakhupha ububi phakathi kwakho\x + 22.21,22. Dute. 13.5.\x*.
\p
\v 25 Kodwa uba indoda ifica intombi eganileyo egangeni, indoda iyibambe, ilale layo, ngakho indoda kuphela elele layo izakufa.
\v 26 Kodwa lingenzi lutho entombini; kakulasono sokufa entombini; ngoba njengendoda evukela umakhelwane wakhe imbulale, injalo lindaba.
\v 27 Ngoba iyifice egangeni; intombi eganileyo ibihlabe umkhosi, njalo bekungelamuntu wokuyisindisa.
\p
\v 28 Uba indoda ifice intombazana eyintombi emsulwa engagananga, iyibambe, ilale layo, babesebeficwa\x + Eks. 22.16,17.\x*,
\v 29 khona indoda ebilele layo izanika uyise wentombi inhlamvu zesiliva ezingamatshumi amahlanu, njalo ibe ngumkayo, ngoba eyithobisile; kayilakuyilahla zonke izinsuku zayo\x + 22.24.\x*.
\p
\v 30 Indoda kayingathathi umkayise\x + Levi 20.11. Levi 18.8.\x*, kayingembuli umphetho wesembatho sikayise\x + Ruthe 3.9. Hez. 16.8.\x*.
